{"timestamp": "2025-12-06 18:26:08.422958", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission result:\n- Anomaly detected: true\n- Faulty device(s): host_2_1_1_1\n- Root cause: arp_acl_block\n\nRationale:\nhost_2_1_1_1 (10.2.1.13) is isolated at Layer 2 because nftables ARP filter rules drop all ARP frames (input/output chains with unconditional drop). This blocks ARP resolution to its gateway and peers, causing complete loss of IP connectivity. Other network components function normally.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2166, "output_tokens": 108, "total_tokens": 2274, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 2048}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
